PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1215 - PRIMISULFURON- METHYL) by setting maximum limits on residues (MRLs) of the herbicide Primisulfuron-methyl that may be present in food derived from animals raised on feed that was treated with this substance or as a result of its use on corn.

Regulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1215 - PRIMISULFURON-
METHYL) by setting maximum limits on residues (MRLs) of the herbicide
